name: TheRestaurantPicker
0:
”Alexa, open the restaurant picker”
”Alexa, ask the restaurant picker who should take out the trash”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the restaurant picker
des: Next time you're trying to decide whose turn it is pick a restaurant or which type of food to grab for dinner just ask Alexa for help! For example, if you're trying to decide between two food choices such as seafood or steak, Alexa can randomly select someone's name from the list to pick for the group. Or if you're trying to decide who should make dinner Alexa can do that too!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
